Author: Tios123
Title: [BOUNTY]*TIO*RE-INNOVATIONG THE TOUR GUIDES & OPERATORS SECTOR-NOW ON ETHERDELTA
Body: GENERAL NOTICE TO ANY REASONABLE GOOD VOLUME CRYPTOCURRENCY EXCHANGES        This is a general open request to any exchanges of reputation out there.        Tio Guides is actively looking for an exchange to be our flag bearing major currency exchange point.        At this point we are only listed on EtherDelta and have not been listed on any other exchanges. We have written some exchanges but we have not concluded with anyone yet. We were about to start a massive promotion about our new super cheap  Domain Registration to domainers and webhosting forums before the Ethereum network pushed up their gas fees to prices that would have been counter productive to any promotional campaign.        All we are looking for at this point is an exchange that we can point our future clients to buy TIO from and fund their wallet.       Here is what we promise to bring to the table.    - We are passionate about our project. We will continue doing this until it works out. We are here as company that will not stop trying until we take our position on the global stage.    - We are not just a token, our project has real life applications. While we may not be very attractive right now to the cryptocurrency community (Because we are not "Quantum Physics"etc) , once we capture the attention of the markets that we intemd to capture, that is a growth potential that will be felt massively through on the exchanges that we are on.   - We are doing our own promotion. Because our platform(s) will be used by most likely people who don't invest in cryptocurrency, we have to promote our products/services to them, and wherever we promote our services we will be mentioning your exchange and asking them to buy TIO on your Exchange and that is free promotion for you. So far we have spent over $40,000 in promotional campaigns and we are only just starting because the biggest campaigns will be once our project is up and running.   - We are a funded company Yes we are funded with restrictions. Our expenses have to be justified and without large risk. So paying $50 to $100k to list on an Exchange of whom those who recently listed are doing less $1,000 a day is an absolute risk that we can not justify taking, so if you require that amount of money for a listing and those who recently listed on your exchange are doing poorly, then we simply can not take that risk.  - We are yet to be listed on coinmarketcap The fact that we are yet to be listed on coinmarketcap at this point is a gifr and a curse. With the backing of a good exchange, right after listng on CMC, we can grow very quickly to over $1 and more. That will bring attention/users to any exchanges that we are on.  - We know the value of money We are building real structures and facilities in the real world and we understand the value of money. Again what this means is we can not just throw around money without justifiable reason, $50k is a good fraction of the total amount of money we need to furnish the current hotel we're building.      This is an open request and we are open to hearing directly from the exchanges not Agents please.     Thank you everyone!

Author: Tios123
Title: [BOUNTY]*TIO*RE-INNOVATIONG THE TOUR GUIDES & OPERATORS SECTOR-NOW ON ETHERDELTA
Body: Before making my next announcement, I want to apologize for the delayed launch of our tour guides platform. The reason is because we suffered an attemped hack on our platforms wallet. Those who may not know, our main mission here is to build a platform for tourist, tour guides and tour operators to easily interconnect and book hotels/tours and other services using TIO.    What this means is that the safety of our online wallet is extremely important to avoid losses when people start funding their wallet and keeping their money on our platform. We have hired some top internet engineers to help us put this together correctly. They are currently working on it, if we think that a completion of a hackproof safe wallet will take much longer, we will launch the platform without the wallet for now, just so that you can be able to see what it looks like, and log in and play around with it. Please give some more to make that decision.    But in all honesty, most people on here care more about profit than using a new platform, regardless of how great it is, and since there will be very minimal demand on our platform for sometime until we grow our userbase, the launch of our platform would have had nothing to do with the value/demand of our tokens. I guess this is the reason why many companyies even with working products are doing badly.    In addition to our Tour Guides Platform, Our Hotels being built, and all the other projects which we have in the works, we have new project which will instantly build demand pressure on our currency.

Author: Tios123
Title: [BOUNTY]*TIO*RE-INNOVATIONG THE TOUR GUIDES & OPERATORS SECTOR-NOW ON ETHERDELTA
Body: We our price has gone up over 4 times since you wrote that, So 1 ETH can no longer buy that much, luckily you took advantage of the price earlier. However our prices are still very cheap, as we are yet to be listed on any other centralized exchanges and on coinmarketcap, so anybody still trying to get in early still has a chance. A lot of the people who hold TIO are holders of very small amounts. so when they put in on the Exchange, I'm pretty sure they put the whole thing in. there's 97k+ in the exchange, thats where alot of the holders are.    TIO has been in the works since 2015, means we have been putting together the company since 2015. First website is that which you currently see, And it was intended to be a promotional website for the token sale. So our first real website, as TIO tours, open for business will be in three days, 25th November. Hannah wanted to have people who she had worked with in the past and trusted on the team, so that took a while to get some of the team members to leave previous engagements to do this full time. The entire members of the team have known ourselves for quite some time now.    Some of the team members have linkedin, some don't. Linkedin is not a very popular platform in Germany and Thailand, and most Germans are uncomfortable with having public internet profiles, you are german yourself I'm sure you understand that. Go through Hannah's Linkedin Profile and you can see the rest of us as her connections.   I don't think google map works that way in Thailand, not unless if it's an address is pinned on google map, most definitely not for an address in Nawamin. Point is can you find Nawamin Road, Soi 24? Soi Means small Street in Thai. If you're at Nawamin Soi, all that is left is to count the house numbers from there. Again send us an email and we'll give you a hand drawn map, to save you the headache of counting house numbers when you're in the Soi.    The reddit thread was basically opened for us to meet the listing requirements for HitBTC, it's obviously not being used and it's not a proper subreddit. We have to create a new one.     You can participate in the bounty.    Have a good day snuggles!

Title: [BOUNTY]*TIO*RE-INNOVATIONG THE TOUR GUIDES & OPERATORS SECTOR-NOW ON ETHERDELTA
Body: really sorry for the suspense guys, but this will be worth the wait.  Our biggest goal here is to make TIO a currency that will become a neccessity to everyday people, not just cryptocurrency users.   Listing on big exchanges are not good enough, even on a big exchange after a while if your token/currency is not a necessity it will become forgotten in this quick changing cryptocurrency environment.   Obviously any cryptocurrency that is not working towards mass adoption, is most likely just here to collect ICO money or waste time.    ...Just give us a bit more time, we will make the special announcement.       Beyond the special announcement, we have some other news.     1. We posted some more shirts, as promised. To those, whose addresses are correct in the bounty form. Siggi should be announcing those tomorrow Asian time.     1b. We are launching a google campaign to promote some the videos which we have on youtube.     2. If you have been paying attention, we promised some viral videos,4 weeks ago. It's read for release. We only just put them up on twitter and fb after making the special announcement, in order not to confuse anyone.    3. In September, we announced that we were working on a partnership with the World Federation of Tour Guides Association, (WFTGA), we are proud that to tell you guys that, it's still on the table, the WFTGA is quite slow with responses, because it's a global non profit organization, with so many top bosses who have to make decisions, but we are 80% sure that we will have an exclusive deal which will support the Tio Tour Guides Brand. WFTGA is backed by the EU.  4. And finally for those of who are excited about making some profit right now, coinmarketcap is supposed to list us in 48hours. That should give some you guys a quick turnover.     All of thses are just updates, None of the above is the special announcement we are about to make.  Just give us a bit more time, we are perfecting and finalizing our presentation.    Thank you guys.

Author: Tios123
Title: [BOUNTY]*TIO*RE-INNOVATIONG THE TOUR GUIDES & OPERATORS SECTOR-NOW ON ETHERDELTA
Body: Hello Doctor, we have been speaking to them about their listing requirement and how affects us at this stage of our project. and their response was more like the 10k is to reduce their workload, and they asked that we give their support guys some time to process the request.     We've spent so many days and put in a lot of effort to try to get to them and it's honestly becoming more or less of a distraction, if they get to make their own rules and pick their own tokens based on how they feel, and also don't have maybe a listing fee for those who are not up to their requesting requirements, then their is really nothing we can do about it, we can't force them to list us. All we can do is wait as they have said. And the last thing we are going to do is start fake buying our tokens to create a fake volume so that the tokens can be listed on coinmarketcap.     We're putting together listing fees so that we can list on some other centralised exchanges.     Please feel free to ask anymore questions.

Author: Tios123
Title: [BOUNTY]*TIO*RE-INNOVATIONG THE TOUR GUIDES & OPERATORS SECTOR-NOW ON ETHERDELTA
Body: Hey Snuggles, we have no problem with getting asked with the hard questions.     I'm afraid the folks at coinmarketcap prefer being somewhat unreachable, you can only contact them through their request form on their site, their bitcointalk contact and their facebook.     The process of preventing anyone from being a whale with us was taken care of during the ICO. No one has that much token to create a possible dump in our system. We have no private unknown whale traders.      "how should this be if you are already in the TOP 20 with 1 ether investment?" I am not sure what you mean by this question.     You have your information mixed up. 1.5 million tokens was sold. After recalculating, we dropped the value of ur ICO to only 586 ETH, and $103,000 was raised.      Only 450,000 tokens will be available for trading until november next year. This is because some of the companies /friends/partners/people who bought the largest amount of our tokens have chosen let them be for now for the project to gain grounds.     Yes our office is on 134/20 Nawamin Road soi 24, Bangkok. If you are planning to visit us please book an appointment first. send us an email to contact@tiotourguides.com      We will be moving to a more savy office on Sathorn road,Bangkok in January, and we are excited to show the pictures to our community here once the move is done.      Our first TIO hotel is currently being constructed and its right next to the famous Wat paryar surin in Bangkok, you can't miss it, there is a big contruction going on there, thats us. And holders of TIO token will be able walk-in and pay with TIO next year, this is one of the many TIO hotels that are being planned     In hong kong our registered address is at Miramar Towers, on Nathan Road, Kowloon. Tsim Sha Tsui.     We are currently setting up a Warehouse/Repackaging factory in Nanchang, China in preparation for our entrance into tech gadgets.     If you really want to meet us in person, we are organising two different events in the coming months this year and next.     1. We are excited to meet some of the members of our community in person, we will be having a lottery draw in late december for our bounty particpants, that event will also be an end of year party, we are going to give out official information on that here once we are settled with the details.     2. We are planning on hosting a cryptocurrency expo in thailand before the middle next year to sensitize the Thai public about the importance, advantanges and disadvantages of cryptocurrency. That would be a good place for companies looking to promote their crypto product to come in and participate. And also a good place to meet and greet us.     It's good to know that I'm talking to someone who reads what we are writing. Most people on bitcointalk don't, obviously because there's way too much going on here.     If you have any more questions please feel free to ask.

Title: [BOUNTY]*TIO*RE-INNOVATIONG THE TOUR GUIDES & OPERATORS SECTOR-NOW ON ETHERDELTA
Body: Sorry for the brief silence.  All questions will be answered now.     Here  is the list to view your stakes and make sure you ethereum address is correct.     https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1j_9WDY2Vj76dLi0_ZeRx-UJovrEBMTRVvOXAaGY9SOU/edit#gid=278609357     It's also going to be now be permanently on page 1 of this thread        Beyond the Stakes calculated, we now have a rewards list.  The Green Dollar Sign after your name means you are in our rewards list, will explain on that a little further in a bit.     Here is how the stakes were calculated ( for those who never asked the rules behind the bounty)     So you are limited to 2 activites each a week. Means 4 activity max, and we have 7 weeks. Like and Tweet/Post, Share/retweet.    So if you liked and shared at least 2 times a week you would have full four activities per week which means 28 activities (act) The entire campaign to the 25th of septmber.      Those who got the maximum full activites for the week that they started from, were given an extra 50 Tio Bonus.       For example if you started from week 1, your maximum activity is 28, if you started on week 2 max is 24, week 3 max is 20, week 4 max 16, week 5 max is 12, week 6 max is 8. No bonus was given for the final week.      If you had more than one account, the accounts with lower activities were deleted and the account with the highest activity was listed.        Again guys, you can only have 1 facebook and 1 twitter account. Anything else is a duplicate. If we didnt find out your duplicated account, please honestly let us know and we'll take it out.             How much you get then depends on how many friends you have on your twitter or facebook.         and extra bonus was given to those who have been obviously visible on our facebook, twitter  and on the threads...and those are the people in our rewards list.     Your stakes are calculated from the week you started, and also when you shared/retweeted the post/tweet.    If you retweet a post thats says ICO ends in 24 hours after 2 days, then it can not be counted for you, as your retweeting is irrelevant.                                                   ABOUT OUR REWARDS PROGRAM    Bitcointalk is majorly filled with finance companies, and it's easy to forget that we are an internet travel technology company.  As we progress further into our project, we want to know those who are on board with us and also reward them and grow financially with, we are a small company with big dreams and community means everything to us.    Our rewards program is a way of saying thank you, and identifying those who we know are in our inner circle.    If you find your name in our rewards program it means that your opinion really matters to us, everybody's opinion matters but your's is very personal to us.    Those who's names appear in our rewards program, are some of the most noticeable people in our project, and on all our social media's, in the comment sections of our post/tweets,they  in the other language threads, some of them are bounty hunters who also invested thier money in this project. We welcome anyone else who would like to see their name in our rewards list to get on board, get active, be helpful on the threads,  and you'll see the green sign  after a while.   Here is what you stand to benefit by being on our rewards,   1. More Tio Bonus Tokens. (We'll occassionally, gift bonus tokens to members of our rewards program)       2. Whatever items we are giving away, Those on our rewards program will be the first to get it, before we start giving to others. For examples, The Technogical items for travel that we are currently manufacturing, (we are not talking about them yet here because of copy cats.) Members on our rewards list, will be first to get and test these items.  3. A possiblity to get free flights/flier miles that you can travel with, free flight upgrades, extra discounts on hotel stays, or free hotel stays, discounts on tour tickets, or outright free tours Extra Discounts when using our platform.  4. When hiring for full or part time job, we'll pay attention to those on our rewards list.  5. There is a possibily to get Tio Loans from us. Very rarely but yes, possible.  6. Allowed access to events that we could be hosting or sponsoring around your city in the future    more will be added to the list as we go on.  What we hope is that as a member of our rewards list,                                                      NEW PRICE CONTROL POLICY  As the crypto community becomes more and more crowded, we believe most crypto traders will start to pay attention to the difference between a Cryptocurrency/token with a community and Company with a cryptocurrency and a community. There is a huge difference between the two - Anybody can create a cryptocurrency/token and list on an exchange and then the survival on that cryptocurrency is based on luck.    While to create a cryptocurrency that will stand the test of time and become relevant requires a serious company, dedication, planning, sacrificies.     Here is what we are trying to say...A lot of you bounty hunters are already collecting all kinds of tokens/cryptocurrencies right? but what you are really looking for is a token that has or will have a good value right?    For any cryptocurrency to have a good value, their has to be price control (economic policies). We talked about price control so many times in our whitepaper, price control is a key part of this project.    For any currency to have a high value, their has to be demand or scarcity. Since this is a new project, demand is what we do not have yet, but what we can create for now is scarcity.    We want Tio to be trading above USD$1 on a minimum and we are looking at $5 to $10 down the line on good days.[/b]       In order to acheive this, we have decided on the following,    This bounty rule does not apply to those who bought the tokens during the ICO or from the exchange. Those who bought the tokens have the right to buy or sell the tokens at will.    This is a very temporary price control, once the demand from our platform becomes strong enough to carry large supply of our tokens, we will remove all restrictions and every bounty member can then trade as much as they want. We will move quickly with the platform and building customer base to drive demand for our services and we believe a lot of you guys will be glad that kept your Tio Tokens.    We will be paying out only half of all bounty payments worth more than 200 Tio, Every monthly payment cycle.  For the half that is given to you, we expect that you keep half (of the half) of the tokens in your wallet at all time in order to continue to receive payment from our bounty. Those who dump their entire half of the tokens that was paid out on the market will be removed from the bounty program,and the balance of the tokens owed will be paid once the price control is removed.

Body: That's exactly what is going to happen...You will be able to book tours/hotels and more with our tokens on our platform... What we are going to do is continue our price control policy, we'll build a huge necessity/demand for Tio Tokens not from traders but from regular people who will need our products/services and however, we'll continue to keep scarcity.         So in the long run 6 months after we start trading, we expect our price to be in the double digits. Now whether or not those who currently hold the token will be able to resist sales for that long is anybody's guess.     Hope you're having an awesome weekend?

Body: Hello Denis, Our Bounty Campaign was a very large one. Almost 3,000 Entries in all  bounty categories and in order to protect our tokens from being taken by fake/fraud entries, we had to manually review every like and share for all tweets/retweets since august.  That means we had to manually review over 1,000,000  activites (Tweets, likes shares, posts,comments, blogs on all our social media). Doing a manual review has saved us a large amount of tokens, if we had used bots as we planned to, a lot of the fake/fraud entries would most likely not have been found.     This has been a really hard work, every single member of our team has been involved in checking this and we had little sleep in the past four days, this has also slowed down our ability to do other aspects of our project. We take the bounty particpation very seriously, and we wanted to have this sorted out. Good news is we are almost done, we have finished reviewing participation on all campaigns but facebook, we hope to be done with the facebook reviews in the next 36 hours, we  will publicly list the spread sheets with the amount payable to each participant and start paying immediately afterwards. We are looking at paying every participant within the next 3 days. That would mean that we beat our own target of three weeks after ICO.     Looking forward, we are looking at smarter and efficient ways to continue our bounty campaign and make this process of data collection and reporting of work,much easier for everyone involved.     Thank you for asking and thank you for your understanding.

Some of todays Biggest Exchanges will be 3rd grade by the time Mainstream Companies starts to Jump on board. The best thing any company with a tokenized platform can do for itself is focus on the product, focus on the consumers, focus on building a brand. If you build customer loyalty, and create a genuine demand for your tokens. The exchange that you are listed on will not be important, because the demand that your platform creates will find your tokens regardless of where they are. And that is exactly what we are going to do.   With governments around the world starting to take a second look at cryptocurrencies and policies, it's fair to predict that most tokenized companies without a "realworld" necessity/demand for thier product/tokens will die off. As a travel/tour company we are a safer bet!       In the meantime, we have a lot of work to do, large number of marketing targets that are yet to be met. This ICO has been slightly a bit of a distraction, but obviously not for much longer.    Here's to hoping that we've enlightened you a little bit!

Body: Dear Tio team, I have been a silent observer of your project from the start.I think its a fantastic idea. I'm very well traveled and I usually enjoy going on tours, but to be honest most of the time, I'm quite disappointed on how tour guides manage,plan and execute their offered tour. We, as tourist have often less to say on how we would like to be guided while taken on a tour. I'm also asthmatic and therefor limited to certain kind of activities. There's no platform out there, that allows you to search for tours based on your personal needs or like you say, preferences. Being able to just search and define your personal tour, with one click would encourage a lot more people to go on tour.  What are you guys planning on doing regarding the issue of  trusting tour guides?

Author: Tios123
Title: [BOUNTY]*TIO*RE-INNOVATIONG THE TOUR GUIDES & OPERATORS SECTOR-NOW ON ETHERDELTA
Body: If you look around your community where you live, or the places you love to go, you will notice that there is that one special place or event, where the world deserves to know and visit. Maybe if people were willing to pay you a little fee, you would take them there.    This is what this project is about.    We are currently making that platform where you can go and announce that special place that you believe others have to see, and for a little fee you can show them that world through your eyes.     This will create hundreds of thousands of jobs around the world (if not millions) and unlock some of the most beautiful places or events that are yet to be heard of around the world    This is an Original idea. Nothing like this has been made yet, and if you're participating in this project either through our bounty or just liking us for free or buying tokens, you're participating in a noble project with limitless opportunities.  We are more about Human interconnection, not just like facebook friends who never meet, but online friends who's sole intent is either create a tour, or form a tour group that tours together. Tour guides who join forces to create tours together, or tour companies that connect with other tour companies, or newly formed tour groups and market their tours to the locals around where the tour company is located.  We can only hope that someday, we'll all look back and remember when this was a small project looked at with a lot of skepticism.    Thank you

Author: Tios123
Title: [BOUNTY]*TIO*RE-INNOVATIONG THE TOUR GUIDES & OPERATORS SECTOR-NOW ON ETHERDELTA
Body: It would be really nice if some of the folks who ask these questions come back to say ohw now I get it, after we answer it. I hope you come back and confirm if you undestand or ask more questions.    Here is an explanative answer to your question.     You really wanted to go on a tour of all the IT universities in Paris, you want the tour to have a native english speaker and have not more than 5 participating tourists. So you google search it and our site comes up. On our site you see the tour guides and operators that are offering the same exact tour you are looking for, so you contact them.  They tell you their price and it's calculated in Tio. You look around and on the top of the site it says you can buy Tio directly with your debit or credit card. So you put in your debitcard information to buy tio and bingo it's succesful Now you have 100 Tio to pay for the tour you searched and found on our site and also have some left for next time you want to get another tour offered by the guides or operators on our site.     No technical Knowledge needed, No stress. Just click, convert dollar to Tio, and Pay.     Please let us know if you get the message.

Body: No offence, but you obviously didnt read any part of our announcement or White Paper. This is about tour guides, tour operators, and tourists who want to use their services for tour purposes.   We are happy to address your concern, although you're quite off from what we're offering. With regards to what you have just said about countries having their own currency, it's actually a very possible and logical business plan for any company or token to have and/or aspire to. And even though Tio is not a Tourist coin, we will not rule out the possibility of us venturing outside the tours sector of global tourism.    So what is Tio about? We are creating a platform for anyone to find personalized tours or create theirs, Tio token will be used on our platform as a payment tool between the tour guides/operators who offer these personalized tours and the tourists who wish to participate in these tours.    Here's something closely connected to your initial comment above, We are getting ready to announce the first roughly 300 hotels/tour operators that will be accepting Tio as a payment tool.(Note this is not an official confirmation yet, an official confirmation will be announced appropriately).   If you had read our website or white paper, you would have seen, that our token will have a sell gate per day, which will be signed and contracted with the Exchanges that we list on. There is no way for any single person to dump the coin in large amount to disrupt the price.    We hope this explanation helped to give you an insight into what we are about!

Author: Tios123
Title: [BOUNTY]*TIO*RE-INNOVATIONG THE TOUR GUIDES & OPERATORS SECTOR-NOW ON ETHERDELTA
Body: We did consider an Escrow, however there are countless cases where the Escrow made away with money or completely frustrated the campaign with overzealous requests, or got hacked and the entire thing becomes a painful waste of time for everyone  So picking one person or two people as an escrow is with it's own fault. What we would have prefered would have a situation where a sort of "Bank" for cryptocurrency could serve as escrow but there is nothing like that at the moment. An Exchange could also be a reasonable way too if Exchanges could start to stand in as escrows for ICO, but also their is nothing like that. Our company will be offering Escrow Services once we are fully operational so, so hopefully someday  in the nearest future using our services as an Escrow, a company going through an ICO process will more options.  What we are proposing is "presumably" better than using an Escrow. Ours is that our faces and names are here, and we are going to be getting our friends and colleagues, iIMPORTANT INTERNATIONALLY KNOWN CELEBRITIES, to come out and vouch for what we are doing. And since this is about marketing our product, we have set very clear set of marketing goals in numbers for which we "have to" meet before we get to trading. That way our progress is trackable.   On the other hand, we have a proposition for critics who would like to verify what we are doing, and whether or not our company has access to money we are claiming to have. There is a way to do it, It's called an RWA. (Ready, Willing and Able).    So we are happy to write out a Ready, Willing and Able Letter to any person or Company, for which they can use to call our Bank directly to verifiy whether or not we do have the money, and if this money is meant to be disbursed to reasons concerning our ongoing project.
